               "history": [
                  {
                     "text": "#### Early years and education\n\nThe description of his birth in the year <htdate0> helps us explain some facts related to the relationship between Buddhism and the Sui dynasty (隋代) (<htcite0>; <htcite1>):",
                     "source": [
                        {
                           "type": 1,
                           "uuid": "9d5ff2be-676d-403a-8f87-20e26614285c",
                           "text": "Xiong, V. C.",
                           "page": "pp. 129, 153 - 155",
                           "date_time": {
